('pnw-shrub-006', 'Thimbleberry', 'Rubus parviflorus', 'shrub', 1, 2, 6, 6, 'Part shade', 'Medium', 'Large white flowers, velvet leaves, soft red berries', '["edible_fruit","ornamental","shade_tolerant","wildlife_food"]', '["Salmonberry","Sword Fern","Vine Maple"]', 'Zone 1-2. Berries very soft (do not travel). Best eaten fresh on site.', '{"berries":"summer","leaves":"(wrapping food, traditional)"}', 'Delicate berries (eat fresh). Beautiful white flowers. Large soft leaves.', '["Pacific_Northwest"]', '4', '9', 30, 80, 1),

